membership:
VIP is a member of the United Nations Environment Programme Finance Initiative (UNEP FI) and a signatory of the United Nations Principles for Responsible Investment (UN PRI), an ambitious and forward-looking set of principles seeking to implement social, environmental and governance issues (ESG) in sustainable investment contents.&#xd;
&#xd;
VIP is an association of people in a European network who see Corporate Governance as a necessary prerequisite for a lively and fruitful financial market with credible ethical priorities and principles of steadfastness: Corporate Governance and ESG demonstrably enhance profits and market liquidity - including the membership in ICGN (International Corporate Governance Network).
